<viewdata model="FubuWorld.HowTo.FubuDocsRunner.WorkingWithFubudocsrunner"/>
<use master="Topic" />

<content:main>

  <pre>
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Available commands:
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    add-topic -&gt; Add a new topic to the project
    bottle -&gt; Packages up a documentation project as a FubuWorld bottle
    build-topics -&gt; Looks for a 'Topics.xml' file in the named directory and tries to generate the skeleton files for the topics in the file
    run -&gt; FubuDocsRunner.RunCommand
    snippets -&gt; Scrapes the entire solution for files with code snippets and places those files under the '/snippets' directory of the documentation project
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  </pre>
  
</content:main>